It's got electric windows.
I'll just put...

59:21.160 --> 59:23.240
GUNFIRE

59:23.240 --> 59:26.880
Go, go, go! Shoot the enemy
in the middle of its face!

59:31.000 --> 59:34.120
Carry on, there's a plucky chap!
Well done.

59:36.520 --> 59:38.400
These carpets are excellent.

