No evidence at all
of the marines' muddy boots.

59:45.640 --> 59:47.480
So, there you are, Mr Needham.

59:49.200 --> 59:54.680
The most thorough test of a car ever
undertaken on British television.

59:54.680 --> 59:58.120
The Fiesta's come through
with flying colours.

59:58.120 --> 59:59.720
Drive safely.

